snippet.title: Swift: FB Messenger - Chat Bubbles With Tails! (Ep 6)
snippet.description:
Today, we're going to finish up the chat bubbles tutorial by creating blue outgoing messages.  On top of that, I'll teach you guys how to create the nice little tail that comes with these cute little bubbles :)

How to create Chat Bubbles (Part 1):
https://youtu.be/bNtsekO51iQ

Completed source code:
https://www.letsbuildthatapp.com/course/Facebook-Chat-Messenger

Twitter: https://twitter.com/buildthatapp
